cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "HUVar (acmg-classifier): Fully local ACMG/AMP variant pathogenicity classifier"
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite both this tool and the underlying
  ACMG/AMP and ClinGen guidelines listed in the references.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "Department of Clinical and Molecular Genetics, Hiroshima University Hospital"
    affiliation: "Hiroshima University Hospital"
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/hnakahara/HUVar"
url: "https://github.com/hnakahara/HUVar"
keywords:
  - ACMG
  - AMP
  - ClinGen
  - variant interpretation
  - clinical genomics
  - bioinformatics
  - pathogenicity classifier
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-05-27"
references:
