      a joint consensus recommendation of the American College of Medical
      Genetics and Genomics and the Association for Molecular Pathology
    authors:
      - family-names: Richards
        given-names: Sue
    journal: "Genetics in Medicine"
    year: 2015
    volume: 17
    issue: 5
    start: 405
    end: 424
    doi: "10.1038/gim.2015.30"
  - type: article
    title: >-
      Modeling the ACMG/AMP variant classification guidelines as a
